Subject: Is IIS is the supported web server for Netwrix Enterprise Auditor?
Description: Is IIS is the supported web server for Netwrix Enterprise Auditor?
What_We_Know__c: The customer is interested to know if NAA uses IIS as webserver. They have been informed that NAA uses Microsoft HTTP API starting from v11.6+
Next_Steps__c: Close ticket as confirmed from the customer
Solution_Comment__c:
Question
You wanted to know if Netwrix Access Analyzer (Netwrix Enterprise Auditor) uses Microsoft IIS as a webserver.

Answer
Starting from v.11.6.x, we are using Microsoft HTTP API as a webserver.
